<script>
item = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("itemlist")),
itemlist = []
for(i=0; i<item.length; i++){
    itemlist[i] = [],
    itemlist[i].name = item[i][0],
    itemlist[i].price = item[i][1],
    itemlist[i].quantity = item[i][2]
}
dataLayer.push({ ecommerce: null });
dataLayer.push({
  event: "purchase",
  'ecommerce': {
    'purchase': {
      'actionField': {
        'id': new Date().getFullYear()+""+(new Date().getMonth()+1)+""+new Date().getDate()+""+new Date().getHours()+""+new Date().getMinutes()+""+new Date().getSeconds(),
        'revenue': localStorage.getItem('tprice')
      },
      'products': itemlist
    }
  }
});
</script>

<script>
var itemlist = [];
for(i=0; i<document.querySelectorAll('.sl-textEllipsis2').length;i++){
    var item = [];
    item.push(
        name = document.querySelectorAll('.sl-textEllipsis2')[i].innerText,
        price = document.querySelectorAll('.trade_sku-item_skuPrice.sl-textEllipsis')[i].innerText.replace(/[^0-9.]/g, ''),
        quantity = document.querySelectorAll('.trade_sku-item_skuNum.notranslate')[i].innerText
    ),
    itemlist.push(item);
}
localStorage.setItem('itemlist', JSON.stringify(itemlist));
var tprice = document.querySelectorAll('.trade_summations__amount-box > .trade_summations__amount-price')[document.querySelectorAll('.trade_summations__amount-box > .trade_summations__amount-price').length-1].innerText.replace(/[^0-9.]/g, '');
localStorage.setItem('tprice', tprice);
  dataLayer.push({ ecommerce: null });
  dataLayer.push({
    'event': 'begin_checkout',
    'ecommerce': {
      'checkout': {
        'actionField': {
        'revenue': tprice
      },
        'products': itemlist
     }
   }
  });
</script>
